      <title>通胀倒计时令交易员不安，英国市场再次下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/uk-markets-fall-anew-with-investors-on-edge-ahead-of-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们对政府庞大的财政赤字的担忧日益加剧，且本周关键通胀数据可能显示价格压力仍然居高不下，英国资产连续第二周下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/uk-markets-fall-anew-with-investors-on-edge-ahead-of-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 09:18:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市因收益率和科技股下跌而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/european-stocks-fall-on-pressure-from-yields-tech-declines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于债券收益率上升引发人们对股票市场估值的担忧，欧洲股市周一下跌，而科技股表现不佳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/european-stocks-fall-on-pressure-from-yields-tech-declines</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 08:18:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
